::DrillBit::

He was in mid kiss when this bot killed Destructor. He broke it and saw
KitKat go for her gun. The next thing he knew her and this bot were
going to talk. He was uncertain of this new bot, but KitKat's wink
changed the thoughts in his mind.
"I'll be in my room," he says to who ever would be lestining.
He headed to his and KitKat's room.

He arrived, and just layed down on the bed. He would rest for a little
wile.

::Hot Rod::

He stayed where he was, watching Feline.
"Magnus, I think we might have to fight. Wether their Maximal or not."
He was ready to fight for his love.

OOC: The following is just to get rid of the transports that brought my
charrs.

Near the old Predicon cave, a bad storm moved in. Lightning struck a
small Cybertronian transport that had been left. DrillBit's ship was
destroyed.

An avalanch in the arctic reagin put K-9's transport under 10 feet. The
heavaly armed ship, was gone from site.
